<h1>Pointstreak.com Schedule Liberation</h1>
<p>Enter the url for the printable version of your teams schedule, select the format and hit go!</p>
<p>To find your teams schedule page:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Visit the leagues home page</li>
  <li>Click on the team in question</li>
  <li>Click the SCHEDULE link under TEAM MENU</li>
  <li>Click PRINT THIS PAGE</li>
</ol>

<%= simple_form_for Conversion.new do |f| %>
  <%= f.input :url %>
  <%= f.input :format, collection: Conversion.formats %>
  <%= f.button :submit, 'GO!' %>
<% end %>
